对图像的每个像素点(-1)**（x+y）¶

In [3]:
def apply_phase_shift(image):
    rows, cols = image.shape
    centering_matrix = np.ones((rows, cols))
    for x in range(rows):
        for y in range(cols):
            centering_matrix[x, y] = (-1)**(x+y)
    centered_image = image * centering_matrix

    return centered_image

计算图像的离散傅里叶变换¶

In [4]:
def compute_dft(image):
    dft = np.fft.fft2(image)
    return dft
In [5]:
image_shift_1 = apply_phase_shift(image_1)
image_shift_2 = apply_phase_shift(image_2)
image_shift_3 = apply_phase_shift(image_3)

dft_1 = compute_dft(image_shift_1)
dft_2 = compute_dft(image_shift_2)
dft_3 = compute_dft(image_shift_3)

plt.figure(figsize=(20,60))

plt.subplot(1, 3, 1)
plt.imshow(image_1, cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')

plt.subplot(1, 3, 2)
plt.imshow(20 * np.log(np.abs(dft_1)+1), cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')

dft_shift = np.fft.fftshift(dft_shift_1)
plt.subplot(1, 3, 3)
plt.imshow(20 * np.log(np.abs(dft_shift)+1), cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
